&lt;div class="col-md-9"&gt;
    &lt;h1 class="display-5 fw-bold text-dark mb-2"&gt;Decoding Cell Death in Disease&lt;/h1&gt;
    &lt;p class="lead text-secondary mb-0"&gt;
        Investigando os mecanismos celulares, moleculares e genéticos da morte celular regulada no contexto das doenças humanas.
    &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="col-md-3 text-md-end mt-3 mt-md-0"&gt;
    &lt;span class="badge badge-decide-green px-3 py-2 fs-6"&gt;Ciência Fundamental&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="badge badge-decide-blue px-3 py-2 fs-6 mt-1"&gt;Translacional&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;



&lt;div class="col-md-4"&gt;
    &lt;div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm bg-white"&gt;
        &lt;div class="card-body"&gt;
            &lt;div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3"&gt;
                &lt;div class="p-3 bg-opacity-10 bg-primary rounded-3 text-primary me-3"&gt;
                    &lt;i class="bi bi-journal-medical fs-3"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;h5 class="card-title mb-0 fw-bold"&gt;Linhas de Pesquisa&lt;/h5&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;p class="card-text text-muted small"&gt;Mapeamento de vias apoptóticas e necroptóticas em patologias inflamatórias e oncológicas.&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;a href="bio.qmd" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary w-100 mt-2"&gt;Explorar Linhas&lt;/a&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="col-md-4"&gt;
    &lt;div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm bg-white"&gt;
        &lt;div class="card-body"&gt;
            &lt;div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3"&gt;
                &lt;div class="p-3 bg-opacity-10 bg-success rounded-3 text-success me-3"&gt;
                    &lt;i class="bi bi-cpu-fill fs-3"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;h5 class="card-title mb-0 fw-bold"&gt;Ferramentas & Dados&lt;/h5&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;p class="card-text text-muted small"&gt;Pipelines bioinformáticos abertos e scripts customizados para análise de transcriptômica de célula única.&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;a href="ferramentas.qmd" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-success w-100 mt-2"&gt;Acessar Recursos&lt;/a&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="col-md-4"&gt;
    &lt;div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm bg-white"&gt;
        &lt;div class="card-body"&gt;
            &lt;div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3"&gt;
                &lt;div class="p-3 bg-opacity-10 bg-warning rounded-3 text-dark me-3"&gt;
                    &lt;i class="bi bi-mortarboard-fill fs-3"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;h5 class="card-title mb-0 fw-bold"&gt;Cursos & Treinamentos&lt;/h5&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;p class="card-text text-muted small"&gt;Workshops práticos de biologia molecular computacional e protocolos experimentais in vitro.&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;a href="cursos.qmd" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-warning w-100 text-dark mt-2"&gt;Ver Cronograma&lt;/a&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;



&lt;div class="col-lg-8"&gt;
    &lt;div class="card border-0 shadow-sm p-4 bg-white h-100"&gt;
        &lt;h3 class="fw-bold border-bottom pb-2 text-dark"&gt;&lt;i class="bi bi-broadcast me-2"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;Destaque Científico&lt;/h3&gt;
        &lt;p class="mt-3"&gt;
            O DeCiDe LAB foca no entendimento profundo de como falhas nos checkpoints de morte celular programada desencadeiam ou agravam quadros clínicos severos. Nosso objetivo final é decodificar esses sinais biológicos para propor alvos terapêuticos inovadores.
        &lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;div class="alert alert-info border-0 shadow-sm bg-light mt-auto mb-0" role="alert"&gt;
            &lt;h6 class="alert-heading fw-bold text-primary mb-1"&gt;&lt;i class="bi bi-info-circle-fill me-2"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;Processo Seletivo Aberto&lt;/h6&gt;
            &lt;p class="mb-0 small text-secondary"&gt;Estamos selecionando candidatos para duas bolsas de pós-doutorado em Genômica Funcional. Veja mais detalhes no nosso Blog.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="col-lg-4"&gt;
    &lt;div class="card border-0 shadow-sm p-4 bg-white h-100"&gt;
        &lt;h3 class="fw-bold border-bottom pb-2 text-dark"&gt;&lt;i class="bi bi-bookmark-star me-2"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;Fatos Rápidos&lt;/h3&gt;
        &lt;ul class="list-group list-group-flush mt-2"&gt;
            &lt;li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center bg-transparent px-0 py-3"&gt;
                &lt;div&gt;
                    &lt;h6 class="mb-0 fw-bold text-secondary"&gt;Projetos Ativos&lt;/h6&gt;
                    &lt;small class="text-muted"&gt;Financiados por agências&lt;/small&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;span class="badge bg-primary rounded-pill fs-6"&gt;04&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li class="list-group-item d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center bg-transparent px-0 py-3"&gt;
                &lt;div&gt;
                    &lt;h6 class="mb-0 fw-bold text-secondary"&gt;Artigos Publicados&lt;/h6&gt;
                    &lt;small class="text-muted"&gt;Revistas Internacionais&lt;/small&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;span class="badge bg-success rounded-pill fs-6"&gt;27&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
